@startuml
title UC reconcile-grants
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<Command>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Aggregate>> Khaki
  BackgroundColor<<Event>> Orange
  BackgroundColor<<Failure>> Tomato
}

actor "Ansible Operator" as operator

package "reconcile-grants" {
  rectangle "GRANT\n(Aggregate)" as AGG <<Aggregate>>

  rectangle "GrantPrivilege\n(Command)\nsystem_privileges or\nobject_privileges, state=present" as CMD_Grant <<Command>>
  rectangle "PrivilegeGranted\n(Event)" as EVT_Granted <<Event>>

  rectangle "RevokePrivilege\n(Command, state=absent)" as CMD_Revoke <<Command>>
  rectangle "PrivilegeRevoked\n(Event)" as EVT_Revoked <<Event>>

  rectangle "PredictGrantChange\n(Command, check mode)\ncovers both branches above" as CMD_Predict <<Command>>
  rectangle "GrantChangePredicted\n(Event)\nsame plan, no statement executed" as EVT_Predicted <<Event>>

  rectangle "GrantPrivilege\n(Command, user and role\nboth supplied)" as CMD_Ambiguous <<Command>>
  rectangle "GrantRequestRejected\n(Event, Failure)\nprincipal must be exactly\none of user or role" as EVT_Rejected <<Failure>>
}

operator --> CMD_Grant
operator --> CMD_Revoke
operator --> CMD_Predict
operator --> CMD_Ambiguous

CMD_Grant --> AGG
AGG --> EVT_Granted

CMD_Revoke --> AGG
AGG --> EVT_Revoked

CMD_Predict --> AGG
AGG --> EVT_Predicted

CMD_Ambiguous --> AGG
AGG --> EVT_Rejected

note bottom of AGG
  GRANT is keyed by (principal, principal_type, object, privilege).
  When the observed privilege state already matches the requested
  state, the runtime issues no command and reports changed=false.

  A single GrantPrivilege/RevokePrivilege command reconciles a batch
  of such tuples at once: one per system_privileges entry, and one
  per privilege in each object_privileges[] entry. Each
  object_privileges[] entry names its own schema, an optional
  object, and an optional object_type (function, script, table,
  view, or virtual_schema) that disambiguates same-named objects.

  Source scenarios:
  specs/ansible_playbook/exasol_grants.feature
end note
@enduml
